ntainer\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 CyberSec Futures. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add subtle JavaScript interactions if needed later.\n        // For now, the design is static and relies on CSS.\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}